Download Docker

Add Dockerfile and .dockerignore in root of repo

Check if docker is running : docker --version

Check if docker operations are working : docker run hello-world

Create a docker image: docker build -t sapient .

Check docker image is built: docker images

Run docker image in a container : docker run -d -p 8080:8080 sapient


To remove docker image : docker rmi imageName

To remove docker container: docker rm containerName